name: COM_03 msri
description: v4w.enko - "COM_03 msri" is a GLB [ AR] product of generative design process from the "virtual strings" algorithm developed to make a research of open colors - organized in special algorithmic patterns. Possible to rotate, scale , zoom, walk in.  The result form makes calm mode during visiting in virtual world thanks to the empty space in between "pointillistic" approach when there is the minimal visuals is necessary to visualize the form of interactive strings. The 3D object is a fixed point in time of the strings motion.
